                            <comment id="68151" author="keith" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 14:45:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lustre runs on top of Block devices generally through a raid controller. It is the responsibility of the raid controller to manager the health of the disk not generally the file system.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Users who need SMART or other disk health information should configure the monitoring they desire outside of the Lustre Filesystem. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
